Make a borrower input interface.

Don't Normalise the database!  Further thought and several blogs indicate
that normalising too much in this case is incorrect.  See:
http://lemire.me/blog/archives/2010/11/29/why-do-we-need-database-joins
Although I have put the authors in a separatte table I've not split into
first, second name etc.  So semi normalised then.

Make it work with DVDs as well.

